scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 5-168 comprise the full Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, starting with the heading 'SCHEDULE' and including all the negotiated terms and elections (Parts 1-5) between the parties. The lines before line 5 are cover/exhibit information, and lines after 168 are signature blocks. There is no indication of CSA annexes or other documents within this span.
